articles.author: Helen Regan, Hilary Whiteman
articles.title: Australia to recognize Palestinian state, leaving US increasingly isolated among key allies - CNN
articles.description: Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese said Monday that his country will recognize a Palestinian state in September, joining a growing list of Western allies as international condemnation and anger builds over Israel’s actions in Gaza.
